    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>if the map is short you can do:</p>\n\n<pre><code>ImmutableMap.of(key, value, key2, value2); // ...up to five k-v pairs\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>If it is longer then:</p>\n\n<pre><code>ImmutableMap.builder()\n   .put(key, value)\n   .put(key2, value2)\n   // ...\n   .build();\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 345995,
